No. 83,

Orig.

Maryland et al. v. Louisiana.

Motions of Columbia Gas Transmission Corp. et al. for leave to file Exceptions to the Report of the Special Master and for leave to reply to the Exceptions of Louisiana are granted. Exceptions to the Report of the Special Master are set for oral argument. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 1031.]
